have to realize that back in the 30s and 40s, when

00:24.480 --> 00:30.409
planetary studies were at their lowest ebb, The 
techniques that were used by planetary

00:31.199 --> 00:34.882
astronomers were very primitive. There was an 
awful lot of what was called physical study of

00:35.022 --> 00:49.655
