of contrastive features that appears to be

25:30.543 --> 25:48.485
statistically significant at small phase 
angles. In the sense that in blue photographs,

25:49.046 --> 25:59.959
things that seem to be well-known surface 
features appear more often at small phase angles

25:49.046 --> 25:59.959
than at large phase angles. And this is an effect 
which is only weakly dependent on seeing and image

26:00.243 --> 26:05.930
